---
// Projects component - Clean and simplified layout
---

<section class="projects section-spacing">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Featured Projects</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Enterprise security automation and cloud infrastructure solutions</p>
    
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Browser Popup MDM Automation</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive cross-platform policy templates and automation scripts for browser management on Windows and macOS endpoints with Microsoft Intune integration.</p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">PowerShell</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">JSON</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">PLIST</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Intune</span>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/aglobaltec-website" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://guides.aglobaltec.com/popup-policy-guide" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Intune Remediation Scripts</h3>
        <p>Production-ready PowerShell scripts for Microsoft Intune proactive remediations covering compliance, security, and performance optimization.</p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">PowerShell</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Microsoft Graph</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Intune</span>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/cda3a49a" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/cda3a49a#readme" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Docs</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Azure Landing Zone</h3>
        <p>Enterprise-scale Azure landing zone implementation using Bicep templates with security baselines, governance policies, and compliance frameworks.</p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tech-tag">Bicep</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">ARM</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">DevOps</span>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/ebd0b36e/" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Framework</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Component-specific styles that complement global CSS */
  .projects {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  /* Minor adjustments to global card styles for projects */
  .card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  /* Ensure proper spacing between content elements in cards */
  .card .tech-tags {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .card .btn-group {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
